⚙️ Bitwise Operators

| Operator | Name               | Example  | Output |
| -------- | ------------------ | -------- | ------ |
| `&`      | Bitwise AND        | `5 & 3`  | `1`    |
| `\|`     | Bitwise OR         | `5 \| 3` | `7`    |
| `^`      | Bitwise XOR        | `5 ^ 3`  | `6`    |
| `~`      | Bitwise Complement | `~5`     | `-6`   |
